{"pin":"BH10973","subcodes":[{"code":"BH10973","anchor":"","first_line":"O Thou Whose face is the object of my adoration, Whose beauty is my sanctuary, Whose habitation is my goal","first_line_orig":"یا من وجهک کعبتی و جمالک حرمی و شطرک مطلبی و ذکرک رجائی و حبک مونسی و عشقک  ","language":"Ara","word_count":"60","subjects":"@prayers (general or uncategorized), @prayer for spiritual recognition, @knowledge; recognition of God, @nearness and remoteness","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#501\"\u003eLL#501\u003c/a\u003e","full_text_parts":["O Thou Whose face is the object of my adoration, Whose beauty is my sanctuary, Whose habitation is my goal, Whose praise is my hope, Whose providence is my companion, Whose love is the cause of my being, Whose mention is my solace, Whose nearness is my desire, Whose presence is my dearest wish and highest aspiration, I entreat Thee not to withhold from me the things Thou didst ordain for the chosen ones among Thy servants.  Supply me, then, with the good of this world and of the next.\nThou, truly, art the King of all men. There is no God but Thee, the Ever-Forgiving, the Most Generous."],"translations":[{"language":"ceb","lang_name":"Cebuano"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"